Class Constraint

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--Constraint
public class Constraint
extends java.lang.Object

Used for the graphical method, this class contains values for a 2-D constraint, only two variables are present in the contraint. This class is similar to the ComplexConstraint class and they should probably be integerated into one class that contains the functionality of for both of them.

Author:
Michael Bochenek (mboche01@uoguelph.ca)
